{"tid":1063542,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Trump Issues First Veto","createTime":"2019-03-15T23:54:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-15T23:55:08.000Z","uid":171273,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"dec2b0fa269f01d8995b0e097d8b2aff14365af1","tid":1063542,"uid":171273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T23:54:09.000Z","msg":"President Trump on Friday issued his first veto, rejecting legislation to overturn his declaration of a national emergency to fund a wall along the southwestern border. The bill had attracted significant Republican support in Congress, a rare and notable departure from partisan solidarity."},{"pid":"6023a52be23793a290f7e13f5801ee5e50302480","tid":1063542,"uid":171273,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T23:55:08.000Z","msg":"全文<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.nytimes.com/2019/03/15/us/politics/trump-veto-national-emergency.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2019%2F03%2F15%2Fus%2Fpolitics%2Ftrump-veto-national-emergency.html&d=hEl8YzVD%2FOsYsQiwoICJnDC6QH3F2wvzJ1VFJz7MVw4%3D&h=0bc0b2c2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.nytimes.com/2019/03/15/us/politics/trump-veto-national-emergency.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}